{"thi-ap6:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap6:0.2":"Sumedhavagga ","thi-ap6:0.3":"Ekapindapatadayikatheriapadana ","thi-ap6:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","thi-ap6:1.2":"bandhuma nama khattiyo; ","thi-ap6:1.3":"Tassa ranno ahum bhariya, ","thi-ap6:1.4":"ekajjham carayamaham. ","thi-ap6:2.1":"Rahogata nisiditva, ","thi-ap6:2.2":"evam cintesaham tada; ","thi-ap6:2.3":"‘Adaya gamaniyam hi, ","thi-ap6:2.4":"kusalam natthi me katam. ","thi-ap6:3.1":"Mahabhitapam katukam, ","thi-ap6:3.2":"ghorarupam sudarunam; ","thi-ap6:3.3":"Nirayam nuna gacchami, ","thi-ap6:3.4":"ettha me natthi samsayo’. ","thi-ap6:4.1":"Rajanam upasankamma, ","thi-ap6:4.2":"idam vacanamabravim; ","thi-ap6:4.3":"‘Ekam me samanam dehi, ","thi-ap6:4.4":"bhojayissami khattiya’. ","thi-ap6:5.1":"Adasi me maharaja, ","thi-ap6:5.2":"samanam bhavitindriyam; ","thi-ap6:5.3":"Tassa pattam gahetvana, ","thi-ap6:5.4":"paramannena purayim. ","thi-ap6:6.1":"Purayitva paramannam, ","thi-ap6:6.2":"gandhalepam akasaham; ","thi-ap6:6.3":"Jalena pidahitvana, ","thi-ap6:6.4":"vatthayugena chadayim. ","thi-ap6:7.1":"Arammanam mamam etam, ","thi-ap6:7.2":"sarami yavajiviham; ","thi-ap6:7.3":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","thi-ap6:7.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap6:8.1":"Timsanam devarajunam, ","thi-ap6:8.2":"mahesittamakarayim; ","thi-ap6:8.3":"Manasa patthitam mayham, ","thi-ap6:8.4":"nibbattati yathicchitam. ","thi-ap6:9.1":"Visanam cakkavattinam, ","thi-ap6:9.2":"mahesittamakarayim; ","thi-ap6:9.3":"Ocitattava hutvana, ","thi-ap6:9.4":"samsarami bhavesvaham. ","thi-ap6:10.1":"Sabbabandhanamuttaham, ","thi-ap6:10.2":"apeta me upadika; ","thi-ap6:10.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap6:10.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap6:11.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","thi-ap6:11.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","thi-ap6:11.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","thi-ap6:11.4":"pindapatassidam phalam. ","thi-ap6:12.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap6:12.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap6:12.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap6:13.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap6:13.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap6:13.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap6:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap6:14.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap6:14.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap6:15.1":"Ittham sudam ekapindapatadayika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap6:16.1":"Ekapindapatadayikatheriyapadanam chattham. "}